{"tid":1391331,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"御藥堂蟲草靈芝好唔好？聲稱全破壁，測試結果僅5%","createTime":"2019-07-31T11:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T12:21:28.000Z","uid":271617,"like":66,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"036dba251488b52826aad6bc4469f438923c868f","tid":1391331,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:43:36.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】市面上靈芝孢子食品五花八門，大多數<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">標榜</span></span>孢子「全破壁」或<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">破壁率達99.9%</span></span>，聲稱對人體療效較佳。不過，消費者委員會測試發現，16個抽驗樣本中，半數的孢子破壁率低於90%，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">效果最差的御藥堂</span></span>全破壁純靈芝孢子，更<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只得5%破壁率</span></span>。御藥堂質疑消委會測試「未夠班」，今日在報章刊登廣告反擊。<br />\n<br />\n御藥堂質疑消委會測試<br />\n對於消委會抽查的部份靈芝產品含其他成份，但沒有在包裝列明，衞生署表示，根據《中醫藥條例》及《中藥規條》，一些例如維他命E的賦形劑是用於防止產品氧化，不一定要註明。<br />\n御藥堂市場部經理黃先生質疑，消委會測試能否驗出真正的破壁率，「如果我哋只係用5%當全破壁，咪好戇居？」他說現時全港沒有一間合規格的實驗室能驗出靈芝孢子的破壁率，該公司自03年起已於屬國家級的廣東省微生物分析測試中心接受化驗，「學術level肯定高過消委會。」<br />\n<br />\n 記者：白琳 鄧凱欣 黃偉駿<br />\n<br />\n尋日喺TVB仲見到御藥堂滴雞精廣告，點解個牌子出曬名差仲有人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafbc0b05fd02bd3326a055de4f0205396b21b64","tid":1391331,"uid":76087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"有冇link?"},{"pid":"3fe2dcc368700b1d3526a916e5c608583b6fbb87","tid":1391331,"uid":271617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eafbc0b05fd02bd3326a055de4f0205396b21b64","tid":1391331,"uid":76087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"有冇link?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:46:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/article/375-3101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fechoice.consumer.org.hk%2Farticle%2F375-3101&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=1286cb54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/article/375-3101</a>"},{"pid":"ad64ab3c6b1669e025e26701db12e38078fbf926","tid":1391331,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eafbc0b05fd02bd3326a055de4f0205396b21b64","tid":1391331,"uid":76087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"有冇link?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"蟲草當年香港電台都有測試過，但已經搵唔番link"},{"pid":"23a33afeb389e46cc6c984da5fd8a3ee947c985a","tid":1391331,"uid":76087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad64ab3c6b1669e025e26701db12e38078fbf926","tid":1391331,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eafbc0b05fd02bd3326a055de4f0205396b21b64","tid":1391331,"uid":76087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"有冇link?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"蟲草當年香港電台都有測試過，但已經搵唔番link"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"老母成人買 俾佢睇下等佢唔好燒錢"},{"pid":"607c583b061abb1e1ab8074b94df03e9d27d2fd0","tid":1391331,"uid":218652,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:50:34.000Z","msg":"[red<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">]國家級的廣東省微生物分析測試中心</span>[/red]接受化驗，學術level肯定高過消委會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你估下香港人信邊個?"},{"pid":"db2f72064827955d59f516645cbd109090a08b65","tid":1391331,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"健康產品 = ON 撚 9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb3bb816a689e29644073c1a0adbf832db93eb7","tid":1391331,"uid":295481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"香港加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390913</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c15981f3b72329cbbe538ac6433a923fef1bc4bb","tid":1391331,"uid":271617,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:56:24.000Z","msg":"推理：為何在同一標準下檢測其他牌子可以得出90%以上破壁率，而只有御藥堂僅5%？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41ab55d4de19bba7ee421f3d914a89b6b2382c2","tid":1391331,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:57:12.000Z","msg":"國家級的廣東省<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbdf2fe1b68e9a5b961cdb40d6a5b2b379751f5c","tid":1391331,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:16:47.000Z","msg":"國家級的廣東省微生物分析測試中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2251f68519512abb65097b54bcec640ef62942a1","tid":1391331,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:16:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b92b6998ee49a382d729ea87afc91f176722f4ec","tid":1391331,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:17:14.000Z","msg":"在5%的樣本中含有大量填充物。廠商意見，御藥堂產品代理商亦交來破壁率達99.81%的國家級公正性檢測機構報告。然而，本會顧問發現在報告附上的圖片中，有多處顯示孢子有堆疊情況，反映檢測時樣本處理不完善。"},{"pid":"9ef5e2f52722918ba0c52e20da3968c0ea34aceb","tid":1391331,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"十幾年前已經有踢爆呢類全破壁係假"},{"pid":"2eb8807aa90140d4bdc38e9795bb8c6a81634daa","tid":1391331,"uid":57329,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"「如果我哋只係用5%當全破壁，咪好戇居？」<br />\n<br />\n1. $5嘅嘢聲稱值$100咁賣 唔係叫on9 係犯罪 係賤格<br />\n2.  消委會嘅測試唔一定喺香港做 以前好多測試都拎過去外國做 咁都冇留意就回應 呢下就真係戇鳩<br />\n3. 廣州測試 戇鳩"},{"pid":"478450fab7c4f2606dee9e592318f99e6d478999","tid":1391331,"uid":33077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:53:41.000Z","msg":"藥箱變左個爛鬼箱"},{"pid":"80e83df6610a50b5ddbe240609d8b7ac69aed48d","tid":1391331,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:40:53.000Z","msg":"國家級的廣東省微生物分析測試中心接受化驗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f33bedc96d2c1ac8ea2037b332bd3d05ca3d50","tid":1391331,"uid":219635,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"478450fab7c4f2606dee9e592318f99e6d478999","tid":1391331,"uid":33077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:53:41.000Z","msg":"藥箱變左個爛鬼箱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:02:51.000Z","msg":"日日食，藥箱都要訓棺材箱"},{"pid":"8a7b60c4369b2e02935905506725aabd2807334e","tid":1391331,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:33:15.000Z","msg":"早已知"},{"pid":"3aa12e21fe6d23e34a726ac24ecb6f11ff8e71b3","tid":1391331,"uid":290370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:42:20.000Z","msg":"如果要食靈芝呢類保健品，市面上暫時最好係維特健靈，其次係金靈芝，因為呢兩間真係用靈芝(即係亞媽拎去煲湯果舊嘢)，而唔係靈芝孢子，因為孢子只係種子<br />\n<br />\n我10幾年前係一間保健品公司做過，我公司都係用靈芝做保健品，所以攞晒d靈芝同靈芝孢子去做檢驗，check左得出結果就係"},{"pid":"ed4232802139c995becd0968da8d8d8c63bbb379","tid":1391331,"uid":290370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:48:36.000Z","msg":"如果要食靈芝呢類保健品，市面上暫時最好係維特健靈，其次係金靈芝，因為呢兩間真係用靈芝(即係亞媽拎去煲湯果舊嘢)，而唔係靈芝孢子，因為孢子只係種子<br />\n<br />\n我之前係保健品公司做過，我公司都係用靈芝做保健品，所以攞晒d靈芝同靈芝孢子嘅保健品去做檢驗，check左得出結果就係用真正靈芝先掂。所以有時價錢真係反映到一切。"},{"pid":"6e7a89d8c8519bfd1d5e0293fa904ad31aa63ad3","tid":1391331,"uid":31389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:02:16.000Z","msg":"你老母就破壁"},{"pid":"8d4549759020a8e4c9e68a04a6823f7c3c719ac7","tid":1391331,"uid":40052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:03:09.000Z","msg":"安慰劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢多人傻應該少數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9880ebbba2ec5637dc9548d6c773831de11e610c","tid":1391331,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84dac6e96aa30d03d05b621f0e3369e5cc8eec6","tid":1391331,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}